dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from https://geo.gob.bo. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS:
1. Created and populated reference name field. 2. Created and populated Admin0 name and p-code fields. 3. Created and populated Admin1 p-code field. 4. Created and populated Admin2 p-code field. 5. 5 records representing bodies of water were removed. An export of these features named "lago_salar" can be found in Supporting_Info.gdb 6. Constructed Admin1-3 p-codes by appending ISO code "BO". 7. Found and fixed 3 nesting errors with Admin1 and 2. 8. Fixed spelling error for Admin2 "Gualberto Villarroel" in 2 Admin3 records. 9. Found and fixed 1 gap error and 1 overlap error.
